        "description": "Unwrap your Crumbling toys from the blister package and take their fate into your hands – literally! \n\nCrumbling is a roguelike where you control your character with one hand, just like an action figure. Move your palm-sized hero through gorgeously crafted toy dioramas and clash with an army of plastic monsters in thrilling hack'n'slash combat. It’s a test of skill and timing as you evade, counter, and smash your way through to the next boss!\n\nCrack open an animated comic book and discover the story of Mr. and Mrs. Crumble, creators of the magical ‘Crumbling’ action figures. Can this sweet couple and their plucky creations triumph against the nefarious toymaking corporation Böse Corp?\n\nFeatures \n\n★ Unique “handheld” VR combat that feels like you’re playing with an action figure!\n★ A roguelike adventure – learn from each defeat and come back stronger than ever!\n★ Swap out different heroes and find a treasure trove of collectibles! \n★ Challenge yourself with spectacular hack'n'slash, fun mini games, and epic end bosses!\n★ A romping story inspired by saturday morning cartoons!\n★ Yelling “Woosh! Bam! Pow” as you play is optional but highly recommended!",
